---

<section
    id="home"
    class="relative min-h-[85vh] flex items-center justify-center bg-brand-bg py-20"
>
    <div
        class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-row items-center gap-12"
    >
        <!-- Text Content -->
        <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left space-y-6">
            <h1
                class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight text-brand-text font-hero"
            >
                Marco Swift and the <br class="hidden md:block" /> Mirror of Souls
            </h1>

            <p
                class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-text/90 font-bold font-display italic"
            >
                A magical mirror, a terrible enemy, and one boy unravelling the
                secret behind his legacy.
            </p>

            <div
                class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center md:justify-start pt-6"
            >
                <a
                    href="#book"
                    class="px-8 py-3 bg-brand-primary hover:bg-brand-primary/90 text-white hover:!text-white font-medium rounded uppercase tracking-wider text-sm transition-all shadow-sm"
                >
                    About The Book
                </a>
                <a
                    href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09N7JRBL1/"
                    target="_blank"
                    class="px-8 py-3 bg-brand-primary hover:bg-brand-primary/90 text-white hover:!text-white font-medium rounded uppercase tracking-wider text-sm transition-all shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
                >
                    Buy Now
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Book Cover -->
        <div class="flex-1 flex justify-center">
            <div
                class="relative w-[300px] md:w-[400px] flex items-center justify-center"
            >
                <img
                    src="/marcoswift.png"
                    alt="Marco Swift and the Mirror of Souls Book Cover"
                    class="w-full h-auto object-cover rounded-sm"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
